    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E46 M3 driver\u2019s car. This example features the legendary S54B32 inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, feeding power to the rear wheels via an M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity under lateral load. Suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While the aesthetic shows honest patina consistent with its 'good' status, the powertrain and drivetrain harmonics are dialed in for peak performance. A visceral, analog experience for the discerning pilot.",
